Alvine Emma Njolle Ngonja (onye bu onye amụrụ n'abalị̀ itoolu nke onwa Mee nke afọ 1994) bụ onye Cameroon na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agbachitere klọb Belarus FC Minsk na ndị otu ụmụ nwanyị Cameroon.
Njolle gbara bọọlụ maka Cameroon na ọkwa dị elu  nke ndị sị̀nịọ na 2020 CAF Women's Olympic Qualifying Tournament (agba nke anọ).
